{"tid":238253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向黎智英擲動物內臟   強記雞粥老闆上訴失敗即時服刑","createTime":"2017-05-11T02:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T04:53:19.000Z","uid":48093,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d5c76d3b3a19bb424d47fa84b5698b0a9d0f7b2","tid":238253,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170511/large/1494466434_0a98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170511%2Flarge%2F1494466434_0a98.jpg&h=884dce17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒創辦人黎智英於2014年雨傘運動期間，在金鐘佔領區被人投擲動物內臟，兩名佔中糾察阻止施襲者離開時遇襲受傷。三名男子及後被裁定普通襲擊罪名成立，分別判囚9至18周，他們上月分別就判刑及定罪提上訴。高院法院今駁回所有上訴，原本保釋的三人須即時服刑。<br />\n<br />\n3名上訴人為被判入獄15周的大圍強記雞粥東主葉永志（44歲）、被判入獄9周的廚師陳國雄（31歲）及被判入獄18周的融資公司助理經理李小龍（45歲）。葉及陳不滿刑期過重提出上訴，李則指自己當日只是拍片，沒有施襲，遂就定罪提出上訴。"},{"pid":"b14efe8e5e6c4a444e1e9dae55b256b2d9c0fdb2","tid":238253,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:20:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0d402959e6e2a7b4c2ba60e3310a562d0412f70","tid":238253,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:22:23.000Z","msg":"李小龍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c286fd9612ad2e3106fe6cdcca490cbbd9d970","tid":238253,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:24:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>李小龍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打撚到d 獄卒爆石"},{"pid":"2c6086f13e6ad1d352f74b0c6529b9ddc7af137f","tid":238253,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:26:03.000Z","msg":"點解拍片既會判得最重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a02c27ea6a50